snippet.title: Alexis Arc Heroes of the Three Kingdoms official Deminia path gameplay | AlphaDio Production
snippet.description:
I have good news!
I've finished Alexis Arc: Heroes of the Three Kingdoms until the very end! With this version, Deminia path and Tower of Heroic Trial become available which also conclude my project. The newest version is 4.0!
